  {
    "id": "the_sample_sessions_volume_1",
    "title": "the sample sessions volume 1",
    "year": "2025",
    "cover": "https://drewprototypes.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/drew-waters-music.com/album_images/chair_cover_sample+session.png",
    "notes": "\nthis is going to be a 5 song ep with some delimitations/confines. taking only four 1-6 second loops, sort of randomly selected and extracted from past songs posted here below.\n\n<br>\n\n1. a bass drum sound from aiken<br>\n2. a snare-ish type sound<br>\n3. a hihat-kinda sound<br>\n4. a guitar or saxophone from belzer\n\n<br>\n\ni load them into the zoia pedal via micro sd card.\n\n<br>\n\nwithin the zoia, i create a 16 step sequencer, triggering a bass, snare and hihat sound for the first three voices. the last voice is a guitar or saxophone sample that i pitch shift, run through the zoia delay, reverb, reverse and other on-board mangling. this one is not sequenced. i \"play\" it live from the zoia box into pro tools.\n",
    "credits": "\n        <div class=\"dw-credits-title\">credits</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">drew waters · zoia, guitar, recording</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">matt aiken · drums and percussion</div>\n        <div class=\"dw-credit-line\">recorded in los angeles and nyc, 4 november 2025</div>\n      ",
    "tracks": [
      {
        "title": "bank 47",
        "audio": "https://drewprototypes.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/drew-waters-music.com/album_audio/the+sample+sessions+volume+1/bank_47_master.wav"
      },
